::Wolveritron::

    He realized the Autoguns and other weapon systems might be on so he tried 
to back away. It didn't work. He went flying as the autoguns hit him, he 
landed on a rock and was nearly put into stasis lock.
    A signal went out to the nearest maximal ship (Cybertronian Fire) to get 
medical assistance for Wolveritron, it was installed on him so he wouldn't 
die. His pride had a way of making him not ask for help.
    "Slaggin program. I'd rip ya out if I could," Wolveritron yelled at his 
program.
